node.text:
https://www.vixcamps.com/programs-2021/the-spirit-of-music-book-club

Join Victor Wooten (and Friends) for The Spirit of Music Book Club, a 5-night event that will provide you with an in depth look into Victor's newly released groundbreaking novel and audiobook ( The Spirit of Music ) You'll learn information and insights that you wouldn't be able to get anywhere else unless you had written the book yourself. This program will run for five consecutive Monday nights beginning June 28th and ending on July 26, 2021. Scheduled for two hours each evening, each night will also include special guests. Held in conjunction with Victor Wooten and Steve Bailey's new website TheBassVault.com, this will be a not-to-be-missed opportunity.

node.title: The Spirit of Music Book Club is Live Now!
